headline: GE and UAG Partner to Enhance CT7/T700 Engine Parts Availability
summary: GE Aerospace's limited distribution agreement with UAG expands the availability of CT7/T700 engine parts in the regions that are not currently served by distributors.

headline: Leidos, Saudi Arabia's National Security Services to collaborate on security screening solutions
summary: Leidos (NYSE:LDOS) and Saudi Arabia's National Security Services Company (SAFE) will collaborate on security screening technology for airports and other ports of entry across the Kingdom under an agreement signed May 13.
